<l>have different meanings [and] sandhi</l>
<l>according to the way they are pronounced.<note place="foot">E.g. <foreign xml:lang="ta">cemparutti</foreign> is either <foreign xml:lang="ta">cem + parutti</foreign> ' red cotton ' or <foreign xml:lang="ta">cempu
